            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Codifique uma condição que use <code>&gt;</code> para verificar se o parâmetro <code>signups</code> é maior que <code>200</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"get_waiting_list\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(signups)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" signups &gt; \" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"    print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Waiting list: \" /><text value=\"{signups - \" /><text value=\"200\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"get_waiting_list(\" /><text value=\"250\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"33\" endIndex=\"49\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Waiting list: 50\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>if signups &gt; 200</code>.</p></body></html>"
